palaute__info: The feedback will be processed by Public Service Info, which provides advice on the use of public administration e-services and identification.
palaute__lomake__kuvaus__legend: If your feedback concerns an error that occurred in identification, please provide a precise description of the point in service use in which the error occurred and the error message that you received.
palaute__lomake__tunnistustapa: Which method of identification did you use?
palaute__lomake__yhteystiedot_ei: No, thank you (the feedback will be processed anonymously)
palaute__lomake__yhteystiedot_label: Would you like the person processing the feedback to contact you?
palaute__lomake__yhteystiedot_legend: If you would like us to respond to your feedback, please include your e-mail address. You may also submit feedback anonymously.
palaute__virhe__viesti_puuttuu: Please check that you have entered a feedback message
